# Group Patient
## List Patients [/api/v1/patients{?include,per_page}]
### List Patients [GET]

View a listing of enabled patients.

+ Admin or Practitioner role required.

+ Parameters
    + per_page: `10` (number, optional) - Enables pagination and set items per page.
    + include: `appointments` (string, optional) - Join relationship data.
        + Members
            + `user`
            + `appointments`
            + `intake`
            + `soap_notes`
            + `attachments`
            + `prescriptions`
            + `lab_orders`

+ Request Example

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {{ ACCESS_TOKEN }}
            X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
            Content-Type: application/json

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

