## Get Patient [/api/v1/patients/{patient_id}{?include}]
### Get Patient [GET]

+ Require Admin, Practitioner or logged in Patient matching requested patient_id.

+ Parameters
    + patient_id: `31` (number, required) - Must be a valid ID.
    + include: `attachments,intake,prescriptions,soap_notes,lab_orders.lab_tests.results` (string, optional) - Join relationship data, dot concatenation supported.
